<!-- ═══ CRITERIA ═══ -->
<section class="section criteria-section" id="criteria" aria-labelledby="criteria-title">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">📐 评选方法论</div>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="criteria-title">如何产生<span>这份榜单</span></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">8 大维度加权综合评分，杜绝付费排名——每个中介无法通过赞助改变位次</p>
      <div class="divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="criteria-grid">
      <div class="criteria-card reveal">
        <div class="criteria-icon" aria-hidden="true">🎓</div>
        <div class="criteria-weight">权重 20%</div>
        <h3 class="criteria-title">录取成功率</h3>
        <p class="criteria-desc">基于过去三年可核实的真实录取数据，包含 Offer 质量、院校排名分布及拒签率。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="criteria-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="criteria-icon" aria-hidden="true">🤝</div>
        <div class="criteria-weight">权重 18%</div>
        <h3 class="criteria-title">院校合作深度</h3>
        <p class="criteria-desc">与目标院校是否具有正式认可合作协议，是否享有内部申请通道或申请费优惠。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="criteria-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="criteria-icon" aria-hidden="true">⭐</div>
        <div class="criteria-weight">权重 18%</div>
        <h3 class="criteria-title">家庭满意度</h3>
        <p class="criteria-desc">编辑团队联系 800+ 真实留学家庭，收集全程服务体验评分，剔除虚假好评干扰。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="criteria-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="criteria-icon" aria-hidden="true">📜</div>
        <div class="criteria-weight">权重 15%</div>
        <h3 class="criteria-title">资质与认证</h3>
        <p class="criteria-desc">是否持有 British Council、教育部认可等官方资质；顾问持牌率及专业培训要求。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="criteria-card reveal">
        <div class="criteria-icon" aria-hidden="true">💬</div>
        <div class="criteria-weight">权重 12%</div>
        <h3 class="criteria-title">顾问专业度</h3>
        <p class="criteria-desc">顾问平均从业年限、国别专精能力、是否亲身有海外学习经历，实测一对一对话质量。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="criteria-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="criteria-icon" aria-hidden="true">💰</div>
        <div class="criteria-weight">权重 10%</div>
        <h3 class="criteria-title">服务费透明度</h3>
        <p class="criteria-desc">收费清单是否公开、是否存在隐藏费项、退款政策是否合理可执行。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="criteria-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="criteria-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌏</div>
        <div class="criteria-weight">权重 9%</div>
        <h3 class="criteria-title">目的地覆盖面</h3>
        <p class="criteria-desc">能否提供多国联合申请方案，签证、入学、生活配套一站式覆盖能力。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="criteria-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="criteria-icon" aria-hidden="true">🛡️</div>
        <div class="criteria-weight">权重 8%</div>
        <h3 class="criteria-title">投诉记录与合规</h3>
        <p class="criteria-desc">交叉核查工商、教育主管部门公开投诉记录，评估机构合规运营稳定性。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Radar SVG 装饰 -->
    <div class="criteria-radar-wrap reveal" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg class="radar-svg" viewBox="0 0 340 300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation">
        <defs>
